title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - PMDG Boeing 737-700 - Install community liveries
description:
In this video we are going to look at how you can install liveries for the Boeing 737-700 from PMDG which has been released earlier this week. Normally you would simply put the livery into the community folder but for the PMDG Boeing 737-700 this is a bit different.

If you also want to give the aircraft a try you can download it from the site below:
https://pmdg.com/pmdg-737-700-for-microsoft-flight-simulator/
